@base = http://localhost:5065

### Health check
GET {{base}}/

###

# ── Basic price calculation ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

### AC01 — P001 (Osaka) drops Construction 10kg → expect 1500 JPY
POST {{base}}/calculatePrice
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2026-05-01",
  "person_id": "P001",
  "visit_id": "V-AC01",
  "dropped_fractions": [
    { "fraction_type": "Construction waste", "amount_dropped": 10 }
  ]
}

